{
  "chapter": 10,
  "chapter_summary": "楚留香为寻找张洁洁的下落，夜间在冷水中沉思时，水面出现了一个神秘黑衣老妪的倒影。她用魔咒般的声音不许他回头，说只有她能帮他找到张洁洁。老妪问楚留香是否怕吃苦怕死，他一一作答。她说起世上有一个姓麻的神秘家族，住在深山山洞里，无人敢靠近。她让楚留香去找麻家并进入他们的圣坛，因为只有他们的活神才知道张洁洁的下落。她警告他可以用尽一切手段对付麻家人，但绝不能让他们流血。老妪消失后，楚留香找到好友胡铁花。胡铁花嘲讽他中了爱情的魔咒，说张洁洁是个小妖精。楚留香执意要去，胡铁花愤怒地质问他是否舍得放弃朋友、名船和美酒。楚留香决心已定，决定独自前往麻家山洞，胡铁花只能眼睁睁看着他消失在黑暗中。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不许回头，否则就永远休想找到她！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "你知道我找的人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你找的是个你本已永远无法找到的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "你……你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我是惟一可以帮你找到她的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "你知道她在哪里？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只有我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "你能不能告诉我？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不能，我只能帮你找到她，但那也不是件容易的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你怕不怕吃苦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "不怕。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你怕不怕死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "有时怕……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但为了找她，你连死都不怕？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我果然没有看错你，你的确是个值得我帮助的人。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我问你这些话，只因为我要你明白，只有不怕吃苦，连死都不怕的人，才能找得到她。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "我……我已明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这世上有一家很神秘的人，有人说他们是从天涯来的，有人说他们是从海角来的，有人说他们来自滴水成冰的雪原，也有人说他们来自飞鸟绝迹的荒漠，其实……其实世上根本没有人知道他们是从哪里来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "你说的是那家姓麻的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "有人说他们姓麻，也有人说他们不姓麻，其实……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "其实世上根本就没有人知道他们真的姓什么。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "他们和张洁洁难道有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你既然知道这家人，想必也知道他们住在什么地方？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "故老相传他们就住在那里的大山上，一个神秘的山洞里，但却从来没有人见过他们，也没有人敢去找过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "有人找过，但却从没有人回来过。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "现在你就要我去找他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不敢去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "只要能找到她，什么地方我都去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "此去若不能回来，你也不后悔？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "到那时后悔又有什么用？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我问的并不是有没有用，只问你后悔不后悔？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "绝不后悔！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "既然不后悔，为什么要叹气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "现在也许会觉得我问的话太多，但以后你就会明白，我问的这些话并不是多余的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "现在我问你最后一句，假如你已知道这一去，永不复返，你是不是还要去？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好，那么你就去吧，去找那些姓麻的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "但我要找的并不是他们，我要找的是张洁洁。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "可是直到现在，你还没有告诉我，张洁洁跟他们有什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "你也没有告诉我她在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我也没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "你告诉我的究竟是什么呢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我什么也没有告诉你，只不过要你到他们那里去，找到他们的圣坛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "圣坛？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "圣坛就在你知道的那山洞里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "那是个什么样的地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "没有人知道，除了他自己外，从没有别的人去过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他们信奉的，是种很神秘的宗教，他们的神，就在他们的圣坛里，那不但是他们的圣地，也是他们的禁地，绝不许外人踏入一步。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "但现在你却要我去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你非去不可，因为只有他们的神，才能告诉你张洁洁的消息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "他们的神？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你不信他们的神？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "我愿意相信，但我只不过是个凡人，神怎么能和我这凡人互通消息？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "别的神不能，他们的神却能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为他们的神，和别的神不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "有什么不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他们的神既不是偶像，也不是仙灵，他们的神是生神，你不但可以看得见神的形象，也可以听得到神的声音。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "我能找得到神？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那就得看你，是不是能到他们的圣坛里去？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "要怎么样才能到他们的圣坛里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "要用你的智慧，用你的勇气，但最重要的，还是要有不惜牺牲一切的决心，你未去之前，就得准备将你在红尘中所拥用的一切全都放弃，然后……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "然后怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "然后你就可以不顾一切，不择手段……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可以用尽一切手段，无论多卑鄙的手段都无妨，只要你能得到了他们的圣坛，看到他们的神，他们就绝不能再伤害你。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "可是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "可是还有一件事，你必须记着。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可以用计谋令他们上当，用棍子将他们击倒，甚至用暗器，用迷药都没有关系，但却千万不能要他们其中任何一个人流血。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣老妪",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只要你身上沾着他们的一滴血，就必定会后悔终生……现在你已是知道一切，你若不去，也必将后悔终生。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那不是魔力！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那绝不是什么见鬼魔力。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "为什么不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为天底下绝没有任何一个妖魔鬼怪能降得住你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你变成这种迷迷糊糊，服服帖帖的样子，只不过为了一件事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "哪件事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你他妈的真爱上了那小妖精。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "没有人去过的圣坛，会说话的神……你真相信这些鬼话？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这绝不是鬼话。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那老太婆是不是个活鬼呢？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你怎么知道她是人是鬼？你根本没有真的看见她。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那老妖精就这样不见了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "难道你从头到尾，都没有回头去看一眼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "开始时你不敢回头，是因为怕她不肯说张洁洁的消息？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但等她说出来之后，你为什么还不回头去看看呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我……我也不知道为了什么！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你这人的确有点变了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不是有点变，是变得很厉害，以前你就算打死我，我也不相信你会变成这样。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我现在是怎么样子？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "一副垂头丧气，无精打采的样子，一副叫我看着生气的样子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那太婆也许并不是个老妖怪，但张洁洁却不折不扣是个小妖怪。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她不是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她不是谁是？若不是她，你怎会变成这样子？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "可是……你也不能怪她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不怪她怪谁？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这究竟是怎么回事，到现在还没有人知道，你怎么能怪她？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "所以你还是要去找她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你真舍得放弃你那条船？那些陈年的波斯葡萄酒？还有你拼了十几年命才换来的一点名声？……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "就算这些东西你全可以不要，难道连朋友也不要？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "其实我当然知道，朋友你还是要的，否则你又怎会辛辛苦苦的来找我？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但你最好莫要忘记，除我之外，你还有很多朋友！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她们天天都在等着你，甚至比我更关心你，你难道不明白？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我也知道你绝不会不要这些朋友，但你这一去，却真的可能永远回不来了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我……我会回来的。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你用不着骗我，那些人的传说，我也听说过，据我所知，世上比他们更可怕的人，只怕连一个都没有。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为石观音、水母、血衣人，他们无论多厉害，也只不过是一个人而已，他们却是一家人，据说每个人的武功都已出神入化！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "传说是传说，其实……并没有真的看见过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "就因为没有人见过，所以才更可怕。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但最可怕的，还不他们的人，而是他们住的那山洞。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "因为谁也不知道那山洞里究竟有什么机关，什么埋伏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "连蝙蝠岛那样的山洞，我都去过，还有什么别的地方不能去？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "莫忘记那次你是多少人去的？若没有华真真，那次你就休想能回来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这次你还能找得到华真真那样的人陪你去么？我……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "就算找得到，我也不能让她陪我去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "因为这件事只能由我一个人去做，否则……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "否则你就永远休想再见到张洁洁了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这话也是那老太婆说的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "所以你准备一个人去，去对付他们一家人，连我都不能陪你去？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你以为你是什么人？是个三头六臂的活神仙？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 466,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但你还是非去不可？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她真的值得你这么样做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "不管她值不值得，我都一定要这么样做。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "因为我一定要找到这件事的真相，一定要查出那个人究竟是谁，你若是我，我相信你也一定会这么样做的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 10,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
